# Windows checks out CRLF by default. Several tests read a source file and
# assert on its text, and the repository's own line-ending assumptions are
# LF throughout, so normalise on checkout everywhere.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.pdf binary
*.docx binary
*.pptx binary
*.xlsx binary
*.parquet binary
*.npy binary
*.pt binary
*.db binary
*.emf binary
*.ico binary
